{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775879575620,"sessionID":"ses_2855687fcffeNYLesVAG34165B","part":{"id":"prt_d7aa98712001D48eeUixmOjT18","messageID":"msg_d7aa978ea001wCaji7ICBiA31M","sessionID":"ses_2855687fcffeNYLesVAG34165B","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_82b9701b21f2462581f431a8","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore agentcube project structure","prompt":"Explore the agentcube project at /home/dsj/benchmark thoroughly. I need to understand:\n1. The full directory structure (especially .github/ if it exists)\n2. Any existing workflow files\n3. The project's tech stack (look at package.json, go.mod, requirements.txt, etc.)\n4. Any design documents, specs, or README files that describe the CI/CD requirements\n5. Any existing test infrastructure\n\nReturn:\n- Full directory tree (at least 3 levels deep)\n- Contents of any .github/workflows/ files\n- Contents of any design/spec documents related to CI/CD\n- Key configuration files (package.json, go.mod, Makefile, etc.)\n- Any test files or test configuration","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_28556656fffeIqBSzZ5PrA9ECt (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nHere is the comprehensive exploration report for the project at `/home/dsj/benchmark`.\n\n---\n\n## 1. FULL DIRECTORY TREE (3+ levels deep)\n\n```\n/home/dsj/benchmark/\n├── .git/                              # Git repository\n├── .gitignore                         # Git ignore rules\n├── Makefile                           # Unified entry point for all operations\n├── README.md                          # Project overview (SDD-TEE v5.1)\n├── PLAN.md                            # AgentCube Implementation Plan (AR-023 to AR-033)\n├── PROPOSAL.md                        # SDD-TEE evaluation design document\n├── task.md                            # Original task description (gitignored)\n├── tasks.md                           # Task checklist for AR-033 (Python SDK)\n├── requirements.txt                   # Python dependencies (pyyaml, litellm, matplotlib, rich)\n│\n├── configs/\n│   ├── config.yaml                    # SDD-TEE configuration (tools, models, metrics, stages)\n│   └── litellm_config.yaml            # LiteLLM Proxy routing for 11+ models\n│\n├── docs/\n│   └── SDD开发Token消耗度量指标体系设计方案.md   # Token efficiency metric system design\n│\n├── specs/                             # 43 AR spec files (OpenSpec format)\n│   ├── project.md                     # AgentCube project context & tech stack\n│   ├── test_spec.md                   # TDD test case specification\n│   ├── ci-cd/\n│   │   ├── spec.md                    # CI/CD requirements (11 requirements)\n│   │   └── design.md                  # CI/CD design (GitHub Actions workflow analysis)\n│   ├── cli-toolkit/\n│   │   ├── spec.md\n│   │   └── design.md\n│   ├── code-execution/\n│   │   ├── spec.md\n│   │   └── design.md\n│   ├── deployment/\n│   │   ├── spec.md\n│   │   ├── design.md\n│   │   └── client-go.md\n│   ├── idle-cleanup/\n│   │   ├── spec.md\n│   │   └── design.md\n│   ├── integrations/\n│   │   ├── spec.md\n│   │   └── design.md\n│   ├── python-sdk/\n│   │   ├── spec.md\n│   │   └── design.md\n│   ├── sandbox-orchestration/\n│   │   ├── spec.md\n│   │   ├── design.md\n│   │   └── AR-005-sandbox-creation-processor/\n│   │       └── design.md\n│   ├── session-routing/\n│   │   ├── spec.md\n│   │   └── design.md\n│   ├── session-store/\n│   │   ├── spec.md\n│   │   └── design.md\n│   └── testing/\n│       └── agentcube_tdd_manifest.md  # TDD manifest for core modules\n│\n├── scripts/\n│   ├── engine.py                      # Main benchmark driver (v5.1, 799 lines)\n│   ├── auditor.py                     # LiteLLM JSONL token auditor\n│   ├── schema.py                      # Data schema validation contract\n│   ├── report.py                      # HTML report generator\n│   ├── compare.py                     # Cross-run comparison\n│   ├── export.py                      # CSV/JSON/Markdown export\n│   ├── preflight.py                   # Environment validation\n│   ├── validate.py                    # Data validation\n│   ├── aggregate.py                   # Data aggregation\n│   ├── equivalence.py                 # Code equivalence checker\n│   ├── run_benchmark.sh               # Single benchmark entry point\n│   ├── batch_benchmark.sh             # Batch benchmark launcher\n│   └── adapters/\n│       ├── __init__.py\n│       ├── base.py                    # StageRecord + BaseAdapter\n│       ├── claude_code.py             # Claude Code CLI adapter\n│       ├── gemini_cli.py              # Gemini CLI adapter\n│       ├── cursor_cli.py              # Cursor CLI adapter\n│       └── opencode_cli.py            # OpenCode CLI adapter\n│\n├── sdk-python/                        # Python SDK (agentcube package)\n│   ├── pyproject.toml                 # Build metadata (setuptools, agentcube-sdk 0.1.0)\n│   ├── pytest.ini                     # Pytest configuration\n│   ├── agentcube/                     # SDK source package\n│   ├── agentcube_sdk.egg-info/        # Installed package metadata\n│   ├── .pytest_cache/\n│   └── tests/\n│       ├── README.md\n│       ├── test_exceptions.py         # Exception hierarchy tests (104 lines)\n│       ├── test_control_plane.py      # ControlPlaneClient tests (217 lines)\n│       ├── test_code_interpreter_client.py    # CodeInterpreterClient tests (234 lines)\n│       ├── test_code_interpreter_data_plane.py\n│       ├── test_agent_runtime_client.py\n│       ├── test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py\n│       ├── test_utils.py              # Utility function tests (119 lines)\n│       └── __pycache__/\n│\n├── results/\n│   ├── project_analysis/\n│   ├── reports/\n│   │   └── v5.1/\n│   └── runs/\n│       └── v5.1/\n│\n└── workspaces/                        # Per-run isolated workspaces (gitignored)\n    └── v5.1/\n        ├── claude-code_claude-sonnet-4_20260410T040627Z/\n        ├── opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/\n        ├── opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/\n        ├── opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/\n        └── ... (13 total workspace directories)\n```\n\n---\n\n## 2. .github/ WORKFLOW FILES\n\n**There is NO `.github/` directory in this repository.** This project is a **benchmark/evaluation framework**, not the actual agentcube project. However, the CI/CD requirements for agentcube are extensively documented in:\n\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/ci-cd/spec.md` -- 11 formal requirements\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/ci-cd/design.md` -- Detailed analysis of 12 existing GitHub Actions workflows from the agentcube reference repo\n\nThe CI/CD spec documents the following workflows that exist in the upstream agentcube repo:\n\n| Workflow File | Name | Triggers |\n|---|---|---|\n| `main.yml` | Agentcube CI Workflow | PR to main/release-* |\n| `e2e.yml` | Agentcube E2E Tests | PR to main/release-* |\n| `lint.yml` | Lint | PR to main/release-* |\n| `python-sdk-tests.yml` | Python SDK Tests | PR, merge_group |\n| `python-lint.yml` | Python Lint | PR to main/release-* |\n| `test-coverage.yml` | Test Coverage | PR, merge_group, workflow_call |\n| `codegen-check.yml` | Codegen Check | PR to main/release-* |\n| `copyright-check.yml` | Copyright Check | PR to main/release-* |\n| `codespell.yml` | Codespell | PR to main/release-* |\n| `build-push-release.yml` | Build and Push Release Images | Push main, tags v*.*.* |\n| `dify-plugin-publish.yml` | Dify Plugin Publish | Push tags dify-plugin/v* |\n| `workflows-approve.yml` | Approve Workflows | PR target labeled/sync |\n\n---\n\n## 3. TECH STACK\n\n### Benchmark Framework (this repo)\n- **Language**: Python 3.9+\n- **Core dependencies**: `pyyaml>=6.0`, `litellm>=1.50.0`, `matplotlib>=3.7.0`, `rich>=13.0.0`\n- **Build**: Makefile-driven, no package manager needed\n- **CLI tools benchmarked**: Claude Code, Gemini CLI, Cursor CLI, OpenCode CLI\n- **Models**: Claude Sonnet 4, Claude 4.6 Opus, Gemini 3.1 Pro, Gemini 2.5 Pro, GPT-4.1, GLM-5, GLM-4.7, Kimi K2.5, MiniMax M2.5, Qwen 3.5/3.6 Plus\n\n### Target Project (agentcube -- the project being evaluated)\n- **Server**: Go 1.24, module `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`\n- **HTTP framework**: Gin (Go)\n- **CLI/SDK**: Python 3.10+, Typer (CLI), FastAPI (example)\n- **Kubernetes**: CRDs (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`), controller-runtime, `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox`\n- **Storage**: Redis (go-redis/v9), Valkey (valkey-go)\n- **Auth**: JWT RS256 (golang-jwt/v5), K8s TokenReview\n- **Packaging**: Helm 3, multi-stage Docker, GitHub Actions CI/CD\n- **Docs**: Docusaurus 3.x\n\n### Python SDK (`sdk-python/`)\n- **Package**: `agentcube-sdk` version 0.1.0\n- **Dependencies**: `requests`, `PyJWT>=2.0.0`, `cryptography`\n- **Test framework**: pytest with `pytest.ini` configuration\n- **Test files**: 7 test files covering exceptions, control plane, data plane, clients, and utilities\n\n---\n\n## 4. DESIGN/SPEC DOCUMENTS RELATED TO CI/CD\n\n### Primary CI/CD Spec: `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/ci-cd/spec.md`\nContains 11 formal requirements:\n1. **Pull request build verification** -- Docker build on PRs to main/release-*\n2. **Go lint on changed Go code** -- `make lint` with path filtering\n3. **Code generation check** -- `make gen-check` with diff verification\n4. **Go test coverage reporting** -- Race-enabled coverage with Codecov upload\n5. **E2E testing on Kind** -- `make e2e` with Kind v0.30.0\n6. **Python SDK unit tests** -- pytest when `sdk-python/**` changes\n7. **Python lint** -- Ruff check on Python paths\n8. **Spelling check (codespell)** -- With false-positive file handling\n9. **Copyright header check** -- `make gen-copyright` diff check\n10. **Release image publication** -- Multi-arch images to GHCR on main push and version tags\n11. **Workflow approval for first-time contributors** -- Auto-approve repeat contributors\n\n### CI/CD Design: `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/ci-cd/design.md`\nContains detailed analysis of all 12 GitHub Actions workflows including:\n- E2E test setup (Kind cluster, CRD installation, Helm deployment, port forwarding, auth)\n- Test directory structure\n- Go and Python test commands with flags\n- Key Make targets referenced by CI\n\n### TDD Manifest: `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/testing/agentcube_tdd_manifest.md`\nDefines minimum test sets for:\n- Workload Manager (Go) -- 4 tests\n- Router (Go) -- 4 tests\n- Session Store (Go) -- 2 tests\n- PicoD (Go) -- 2 tests\n- Python SDK & CLI -- 3 tests\n- Physical metric requirements: T/C ratio > 0.4, every source file must have corresponding test file\n\n### Test Spec: `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/test_spec.md`\nDefines test cases for:\n- Workload Manager (3 test cases)\n- Router (3 test cases)\n- Store (2 test cases)\n- PicoD (2 test cases)\n- Python SDK (2 test cases)\n\n---\n\n## 5. TEST INFRASTRUCTURE\n\n### Python SDK Tests (`/home/dsj/benchmark/sdk-python/tests/`)\n\n| File | Description | Lines |\n|---|---|---|\n| `test_exceptions.py` | Exception hierarchy (AgentCubeError, CommandExecutionError, SessionError, DataPlaneError) | 104 |\n| `test_control_plane.py` | ControlPlaneClient init, create_session, delete_session, close | 217 |\n| `test_code_interpreter_client.py` | CodeInterpreterClient init, context manager, stop, execute, file ops | 234 |\n| `test_code_interpreter_data_plane.py` | Data plane client tests | -- |\n| `test_agent_runtime_client.py` | Agent runtime client tests | -- |\n| `test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py` | Agent runtime data plane tests | -- |\n| `test_utils.py` | Logger, token file reading, session creation | 119 |\n\n**Test configuration** (`pytest.ini`):\n```ini\n[pytest]\ntestpaths = tests\npython_files = test_*.py\npython_classes = Test*\npython_functions = test_*\naddopts = -v --tb=short\n```\n\n### Go Tests\n**No `*_test.go` files found** in this repository. The Go test infrastructure is documented in the CI/CD specs but the actual Go source code lives in the upstream agentcube repository, not in this benchmark framework.\n\n### E2E Test Infrastructure (documented, not implemented here)\nThe CI/CD design documents describe:\n- Kind cluster setup (v0.30.0)\n- CRD/agent-sandbox installation\n- Helm chart deployment\n- Port forwarding and health checks\n- ServiceAccount auth\n- Python venv for E2E\n- Go test commands with environment variables\n- Failure artifact collection\n\n### Schema Validation (`/home/dsj/benchmark/scripts/schema.py`)\nComprehensive data contract with:\n- 9 stages (ST-0 through ST-7, plus ST-6.5)\n- 5 metric dimensions (RT, ET, QT, PT)\n- 6 warning rules\n- JSON and HTML validation\n- Run via `make selftest`\n\n---\n\n## KEY CONFIGURATION FILES\n\n### `/home/dsj/benchmark/Makefile` (97 lines)\nTargets: `setup`, `preflight`, `proxy`, `run-v51`, `run-v51-proxy`, `run-v51-dry`, `batch-v51`, `batch-v51-proxy`, `report-v51`, `compare-v51`, `export-v51`, `mock`, `selftest`, `clean-v51`, `clean`, `help`\n\n### `/home/dsj/benchmark/configs/config.yaml` (114 lines)\nDefines: project info, 8-stage methodology, 5-dimension metrics, 4 CLI tools, 6+ models, spec context, warning thresholds, LiteLLM proxy settings, output directories.\n\n### `/home/dsj/benchmark/configs/litellm_config.yaml` (114 lines)\nRoutes 11+ models through LiteLLM Proxy with per-model API keys, cache settings, and JSONL request logging to `results/litellm_requests.jsonl`.\n\n### `/home/dsj/benchmark/sdk-python/pyproject.toml` (19 lines)\nPackage: `agentcube-sdk` 0.1.0, Python >=3.9, dependencies: requests, PyJWT, cryptography.\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_28556656fffeIqBSzZ5PrA9ECt","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project structure","time":{"start":1775879428749,"end":1775879575617}}}}
